metadata.name: The Envy
metadata.description: The Envy - the killer in this NFT industry. Who can ever sure that they've never envy with someone in this life. But remember, Envy is not always bad, it's okay to be envy with someone because there will be motivation for you to complete yourself. But, don't ever compare yourself to anyone else. You is you, they are them. Don't try to become someone else that not yourself.
